Before generating, reflect their answers back in 3–5 sentences:

> "Based on what you've said:
> - Your anchor is [X]. The version of you in 5 years is [their one-liner, slightly polished].
> - Your strongest current pillar seems to be [X]; the biggest gap is [Y].
> - Your working style suggests you do best when [observation from Q5].
> - Your 1-year priorities are: [list by pillar — brief].
